1
00:00:14,980 --> 00:00:15,950
Gray!

2
00:00:16,410 --> 00:00:21,260
If you've really betrayed Fairy Tail, 
then you must have some reason!

3
00:00:21,260 --> 00:00:22,650
No reason.

4
00:00:23,020 --> 00:00:24,580
Nothin' like that.

5
00:00:24,580 --> 00:00:25,730
What?

6
00:00:26,430 --> 00:00:27,440
Gray...

7
00:01:59,690 --> 00:02:01,390
Yes-yes-yes!

8
00:02:01,390 --> 00:02:07,070
And now all my research has come to 
fruition, and I have completed my Dragonoid!

9
00:02:07,070 --> 00:02:10,770
Shouldn't you people be singing 
my praises or something?

10
00:02:10,770 --> 00:02:13,260
Is that the voice of this Daphne person?

11
00:02:13,260 --> 00:02:15,480
Give us Natsu back this instant!

12
00:02:15,870 --> 00:02:18,340
Sorry, but no can do.

13
00:02:18,340 --> 00:02:23,790
I'm sure you realize that my Dragonoid here 
moves by sucking out Natsu Dragneel's magic power.

14
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:29,160
Sucking out my magic power?

15
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:33,390
Friendship will overcome the dead.

16
00:02:36,430 --> 00:02:38,850
Until I've sucked out all that magic power,

17
00:02:38,850 --> 00:02:41,940
I ain't givin' Natsu Dragneel back!

18
00:02:41,940 --> 00:02:45,950
To a wizard, one's magic 
power is their very life!

19
00:02:45,950 --> 00:02:47,820
Give back Natsu now!

20
00:02:47,820 --> 00:02:50,340
So, what are we going to do?

21
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:51,690
At this rate...

22
00:02:52,940 --> 00:02:55,670
Screw this!

23
00:02:59,320 --> 00:03:01,350
Yes-yes-yes...

24
00:03:01,350 --> 00:03:04,180
As long as you keep up the good work,

25
00:03:05,510 --> 00:03:07,350
we'll be fully charged in no time.

26
00:03:07,350 --> 00:03:11,160
Then, my Dragonoid will be 
operational for half an eternity!

27
00:03:13,820 --> 00:03:16,580
You want to get in her way? Just try it.

28
00:03:16,580 --> 00:03:19,370
Although even with your powers combined,

29
00:03:19,370 --> 00:03:22,340
I highly doubt you can hold out long 
enough to see it fully charged.

30
00:03:23,190 --> 00:03:24,170
Gray...

31
00:03:25,190 --> 00:03:32,560
I've heard of a dangerous, dragon-crazed wizard 
who was trying to create an artificial dragon...

32
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:34,440
Is that you?

33
00:03:34,900 --> 00:03:38,260
Such slanderous rumors... 
So far from the truth.

34
00:03:38,260 --> 00:03:44,280
They should say "the genius scientist Daphne 
succeeded in creating an artificial dragon."

35
00:03:45,690 --> 00:03:47,910
Artificial dragon?

36
00:03:48,880 --> 00:03:50,000
Could it be...

37
00:03:50,290 --> 00:03:52,450
The egg remains I found back then...

38
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:58,750
It was truly a long struggle 
for me to perfect it.

39
00:04:00,480 --> 00:04:06,460
It all started with the first step: 
Successfully hatching an artificial dragon from an egg.

40
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:14,240
The city I lived in was the perfect 
place to gather data, or so I thought.

41
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:19,550
But the people who come from my 
city can all use Hidden, see.

42
00:04:19,550 --> 00:04:24,850
Unable to experiment on the 
city, I had no more use for it.

43
00:04:26,550 --> 00:04:30,830
Yes-yes-yes! If you like playing 
hide-and-go-seek so much...

44
00:04:31,710 --> 00:04:33,990
...hide for the rest of your lives.

45
00:04:39,050 --> 00:04:42,670
As punishment, I made it so they 
could not dispel their Hidden.

46
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:47,220
I also punished the incomplete 
dragons who were unable

47
00:04:47,220 --> 00:04:50,640
to sense the people who had 
vanished with their Hidden.

48
00:05:01,830 --> 00:05:05,340
Back then? When I went to that city...

49
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:06,460
That voice...

50
00:05:06,460 --> 00:05:07,740
Is that Igneel?

51
00:05:07,740 --> 00:05:10,160
Wait! Answer me!

52
00:05:10,160 --> 00:05:11,640
Igneel!

53
00:05:15,180 --> 00:05:17,760
After that, I left the city.

54
00:05:19,330 --> 00:05:22,160
Igneel, where are you?

55
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,930
Igneel!

56
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:29,880
Ever since then, it became known 
as the "City without Sound".

57
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:36,810
I continued my research, and 
finally it dawned on me.

58
00:05:37,490 --> 00:05:42,000
I needed the power of a Dragon 
Slayer to activate the Dragonoid.

59
00:05:42,570 --> 00:05:45,250
Yes-yes-yes, Natsu Dragneel!

60
00:05:45,250 --> 00:05:47,280
Salamander!

61
00:05:47,280 --> 00:05:49,750
Keep working until you drop dead!

62
00:05:49,750 --> 00:05:52,330
For me, and my evil ambitions!

63
00:05:52,330 --> 00:05:54,330
Get fired up!

64
00:06:01,810 --> 00:06:04,190
What are you doing? That's dangerous!

65
00:06:04,190 --> 00:06:07,270
Looks like it's not just big, it's 
also gonna be seriously tough!

66
00:06:07,270 --> 00:06:08,200
Aye...

67
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,090
You fiend!

68
00:06:09,090 --> 00:06:12,560
What are you planning to do 
by creating such a thing?

69
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:14,050
Yes-yes-yes.

70
00:06:14,050 --> 00:06:18,340
My great ambition is to complete 
the perfect Dragonoid!

71
00:06:18,340 --> 00:06:21,020
Even this is nothing more than a prototype.

72
00:06:21,510 --> 00:06:25,400
First up, we have to test 
its current ability! Test!!

73
00:06:27,400 --> 00:06:30,620
Lower half's mobility is 
sub-par, I see. Yes-yes.

74
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:32,990
Walking is impossible, say?

75
00:06:32,990 --> 00:06:36,510
She's trouble! She's really big trouble!

76
00:06:36,510 --> 00:06:40,440
Ooh, I know! She's what they 
call a "Mad Scientist"!

77
00:06:40,440 --> 00:06:42,000
We must stop it somehow.

78
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:42,940
But...

79
00:06:42,940 --> 00:06:46,800
With Natsu-san inside, we 
can't just attack carelessly!

80
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:49,330
Oh, does it really matter?

81
00:06:49,330 --> 00:06:50,430
Carla!

82
00:06:52,970 --> 00:06:54,230
Gray...

83
00:06:54,500 --> 00:06:56,680
Is this what you wished for?

84
00:07:00,300 --> 00:07:01,710
Gray, you bastard!

85
00:07:01,710 --> 00:07:04,150
You've gone and done it this time!

86
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:07,530
As I am a Man, I will bring 
you back to the guild!

87
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,530
Don't think ill of me.

88
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:16,460
This is Master's orders.

89
00:07:16,460 --> 00:07:17,540
That master?

90
00:07:17,540 --> 00:07:21,630
Yeah. Looks like he got word of Daphne.

91
00:07:21,630 --> 00:07:26,670
He's decided to ask Gray how 
to get rid of that giant thing.

92
00:07:26,950 --> 00:07:28,080
Erza!

93
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:31,990
Wait... Don't tell me... It's...

94
00:07:39,450 --> 00:07:41,140
It's flying!

95
00:07:41,140 --> 00:07:43,020
Flying? That's so unfair!

96
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:44,530
Like you can complain.

97
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:50,780
Oh, no... It's heading straight for Magnolia!

98
00:07:51,210 --> 00:07:52,350
How dare she...

99
00:07:52,700 --> 00:07:57,830
It's already too late for 
anyone to stop my Dragonoid.

100
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:04,460
Lucy and the rest of you return to 
the guild and get everyone mobilized.

101
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:07,180
We'll protect Magnolia, everyone.

102
00:08:07,850 --> 00:08:09,710
But, what would happen to...

103
00:08:10,840 --> 00:08:13,720
I will stop that Dragonoid!

104
00:08:15,470 --> 00:08:16,880
Understood.

105
00:08:16,880 --> 00:08:18,230
Let's go, Happy!

106
00:08:18,230 --> 00:08:19,140
Aye, sir!

107
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:22,640
Gray... What could it be?

108
00:08:27,410 --> 00:08:30,400
I will do all that I can.

109
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,680
You deal with Gray, okay?

110
00:08:34,680 --> 00:08:35,750
Aye, sir!

111
00:08:35,750 --> 00:08:38,060
And you take care of Natsu, 'kay?

112
00:08:38,060 --> 00:08:39,240
Your word as a Man!

113
00:08:40,300 --> 00:08:41,410
Leave him to me.

114
00:08:44,660 --> 00:08:46,170
Stop!

115
00:08:48,130 --> 00:08:49,170
That thing again?

116
00:08:49,170 --> 00:08:51,550
His name is "Lizardman".

117
00:08:52,420 --> 00:08:53,580
Requip!

118
00:08:57,050 --> 00:09:00,310
An artificial creature that 
mimics people's attributes?

119
00:09:02,270 --> 00:09:07,850
Even if you have the same attributes 
as I, you don't carry the same burdens!

120
00:09:09,020 --> 00:09:11,820
Yes-yes... Good for you.

121
00:09:11,820 --> 00:09:14,130
But how about this?

122
00:09:17,160 --> 00:09:21,080
I've made sure to take careful records 
of the previous battle's data.

123
00:09:21,490 --> 00:09:25,600
You'll soon find out the 
power of my Lizardmen v. 2.5!

124
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:28,960
Titania... Erza Scarlet!

125
00:09:37,250 --> 00:09:38,840
What the hell?

126
00:09:38,840 --> 00:09:40,310
Everyone okay?

127
00:09:40,310 --> 00:09:41,600
Yeah, somehow.

128
00:09:43,380 --> 00:09:47,400
I see. These are the spiky 
fellows Erza talked about.

129
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:49,940
Came to take Gray back, have we?

130
00:09:49,940 --> 00:09:52,810
Looks more like they're 
here to wipe us all out!

131
00:09:52,810 --> 00:09:55,860
A Man will repel the enemy!

132
00:09:55,860 --> 00:09:57,000
This'll be fun!

133
00:09:57,000 --> 00:09:58,700
Let's rumble!

134
00:10:00,110 --> 00:10:01,490
Here I come!

135
00:10:02,190 --> 00:10:03,410
Man!

136
00:10:03,410 --> 00:10:06,200
Don't panic! Take shelter in Fairy Tail!

137
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:08,790
Everyone! This way!

138
00:10:09,310 --> 00:10:13,060
So that's the Dragon-thing 
that Lucy mentioned?

139
00:10:13,060 --> 00:10:15,460
The city's gonna be destroyed at this rate!

140
00:10:15,460 --> 00:10:18,090
We can't guarantee that the 
guild will be safe, either...

141
00:10:18,090 --> 00:10:20,770
Does the master know about this?

142
00:10:20,770 --> 00:10:23,790
He went to gather everyone from the guild.

143
00:10:23,790 --> 00:10:27,230
The bunch that went to capture 
Gray ain't come back either!

144
00:10:27,230 --> 00:10:29,220
What the heck is going on?

145
00:10:29,740 --> 00:10:30,850
Elfman...

146
00:10:36,990 --> 00:10:39,360
Man, what a hard head!

147
00:10:39,360 --> 00:10:42,950
Beast Arm... Iron Bull!

148
00:10:44,490 --> 00:10:46,790
Smoke Rush!

149
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:52,500
That's a Smoke Fake?

150
00:10:52,500 --> 00:10:54,040
That's my magic!

151
00:10:57,810 --> 00:11:01,800
Damn it... I've lost my touch... I'm sorry.

152
00:11:01,800 --> 00:11:03,300
Wakaba!

153
00:11:14,280 --> 00:11:16,230
You're not gettin' him back!

154
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:21,490
He's heavy...

155
00:11:27,550 --> 00:11:32,830
Damn it all... Were you really working 
with them behind the scenes, Gray?

156
00:11:33,770 --> 00:11:37,200
I've been saved by Natsu countless times...

157
00:11:37,590 --> 00:11:39,340
When I screwed up on a job...

158
00:11:40,340 --> 00:11:42,700
Ever since he was a kid, 
he had a smart mouth,

159
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:44,770
and never thought about 
consequences to his actions.

160
00:11:45,220 --> 00:11:46,850
But...

161
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:48,720
But... Even so...

162
00:11:50,190 --> 00:11:53,110
For shame, Gray...

163
00:11:58,940 --> 00:12:03,200
For a Man, what matters is 
how he takes responsibility!

164
00:12:03,870 --> 00:12:06,920
And I'll see to it that Gray 
takes responsibility for this!

165
00:12:07,410 --> 00:12:11,330
Take Over: Beast Soul!

166
00:12:25,060 --> 00:12:27,220
Yes-yes-yes...

167
00:12:27,690 --> 00:12:29,890
What a beautiful city.

168
00:12:29,890 --> 00:12:34,510
I'm getting chills up my spine just thinking 
about how fun it'll be to pulverize it!

169
00:12:34,510 --> 00:12:38,440
So sit there in your box seat 
and watch the fireworks!

170
00:12:38,440 --> 00:12:42,570
Assuming you even have the 
strength to do that...

171
00:12:47,370 --> 00:12:50,610
Damn it... I can't move...

172
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:54,860
Natsu... Natsu, the Dragon Slayer...

173
00:12:56,590 --> 00:12:57,680
That voice...

174
00:12:58,240 --> 00:13:00,130
I know I've heard it somewhere...

175
00:13:00,500 --> 00:13:02,080
Young man.

176
00:13:07,400 --> 00:13:10,340
Huh? The pot's talking?

177
00:13:10,340 --> 00:13:14,650
We are the people who live in this city.

178
00:13:14,650 --> 00:13:15,390
How do you do?

179
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:18,440
You're just a shadow!

180
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:20,430
No, no...

181
00:13:20,430 --> 00:13:24,650
Because of a magic called Hidden, 
you can't see our bodies anymore!

182
00:13:24,650 --> 00:13:26,680
Huh? I don't get it.

183
00:13:26,680 --> 00:13:29,110
Then just undo the magic, right?

184
00:13:29,110 --> 00:13:32,790
We called out to you 
because we can't do that.

185
00:13:32,790 --> 00:13:34,680
Who are you?

186
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:35,450
Me?

187
00:13:35,450 --> 00:13:39,920
I'm a Fairy Tail Wizard! I'm 
the Dragon Slayer, Natsu!

188
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:43,740
What?! A Dragon Slayer? Seriously?

189
00:13:43,740 --> 00:13:45,310
I ain't gonna lie.

190
00:13:45,310 --> 00:13:47,510
And you don't have to be <i>that</i> surprised.

191
00:13:47,510 --> 00:13:50,800
Natsu... Natsu, the Dragon Slayer.

192
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:53,010
Please, rid us of this magic curse!

193
00:13:53,850 --> 00:13:55,640
Sure, I guess...

194
00:13:55,920 --> 00:13:57,320
What should I do?

195
00:13:57,720 --> 00:13:59,930
Like destroy the wall?

196
00:13:59,930 --> 00:14:03,400
No. You must defeat the 
one who controls dragons.

197
00:14:03,400 --> 00:14:05,900
Huh? What are you blabbing about?

198
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:09,210
No one can control a dragon! Are you nuts?

199
00:14:09,880 --> 00:14:13,200
But if there is someone 
like that, I'll beat 'em.

200
00:14:13,200 --> 00:14:15,060
Will you promise?

201
00:14:15,360 --> 00:14:17,510
Yeah. It's a promise.

202
00:14:18,780 --> 00:14:20,500
Then, we'll wait.

203
00:14:21,450 --> 00:14:23,500
We will place our hopes with you.

204
00:14:24,560 --> 00:14:28,020
We will always be waiting...

205
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,500
Huh?

206
00:14:31,770 --> 00:14:32,980
Hey!

207
00:14:33,460 --> 00:14:35,580
Where'd you go?

208
00:14:37,120 --> 00:14:41,300
I thought it was a dream or something, 
so I'd completely forgotten.

209
00:14:42,660 --> 00:14:45,150
Defeat the one who controls dragons...

210
00:14:45,520 --> 00:14:48,700
Crap... So this is what they meant?

211
00:14:49,800 --> 00:14:53,280
Well, I promised, didn't I?!

212
00:14:54,490 --> 00:14:57,580
Natsu Dragneel's power's 
grown higher than my data!

213
00:15:00,130 --> 00:15:03,680
At this rate, my Dragonoid 
will go into overdrive!

214
00:15:06,640 --> 00:15:07,960
What was that?

215
00:15:11,230 --> 00:15:12,430
Natsu...

216
00:15:15,260 --> 00:15:18,210
I ain't gonna lose!

217
00:15:18,210 --> 00:15:19,510
Yes-yes-yes...

218
00:15:19,510 --> 00:15:21,800
At times like this, if I 
calmly and meticulously

219
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:24,810
keep sucking up your magic at 
a reasonable pace, then AOK.

220
00:15:25,350 --> 00:15:29,620
Yes-yes, excellent work. Thank 
you for the lovely magic power!

221
00:15:29,620 --> 00:15:30,610
Damn it...

222
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:33,770
Give me a break here!

223
00:15:38,090 --> 00:15:41,370
We've got trouble! Elfman and 
the others came back, but...

224
00:15:43,430 --> 00:15:44,580
Elfman!

225
00:15:45,000 --> 00:15:46,930
Take Wakaba and Macao to the back!

226
00:15:46,930 --> 00:15:48,210
See to them!

227
00:15:48,210 --> 00:15:49,880
Are you okay? What happened?

228
00:15:50,400 --> 00:15:55,510
Nee-chan... Take it from here... Save Natsu!

229
00:15:56,410 --> 00:15:57,680
He's...

230
00:16:00,790 --> 00:16:03,230
I'm sorry... I...

231
00:16:03,480 --> 00:16:05,400
I killed Lisanna...

232
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:11,880
I should have brought you with us!

233
00:16:12,350 --> 00:16:14,230
Then this wouldn't have...

234
00:16:14,230 --> 00:16:15,420
Quit it already!

235
00:16:15,990 --> 00:16:17,990
Stop bawling all over yourself!

236
00:16:18,680 --> 00:16:22,430
If you keep moping around like that forever,

237
00:16:22,880 --> 00:16:25,030
that ain't gonna make Lisanna smile, will it?

238
00:16:25,810 --> 00:16:27,150
Lisanna...

239
00:16:28,060 --> 00:16:31,390
She was always smiling, no matter what.

240
00:16:31,760 --> 00:16:36,820
She was smiling until the very end.

241
00:16:37,680 --> 00:16:43,730
I'm sure that's the way 
she was! That's Lisanna!

242
00:16:44,690 --> 00:16:47,060
It's the sad times when she smiled even more!

243
00:16:48,480 --> 00:16:51,730
Isn't that what they call being a man?!

244
00:16:55,270 --> 00:16:56,630
A Man...

245
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:04,370
Okay. Leave Natsu to me.

246
00:17:07,000 --> 00:17:08,060
Elfman!

247
00:17:08,310 --> 00:17:10,710
I'll heal him with my Sky Magic!

248
00:17:10,710 --> 00:17:12,140
Please, Wendy.

249
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:19,150
Hey! You awake, Gray?

250
00:17:19,150 --> 00:17:21,430
Tell us what the hell's going on here!

251
00:17:22,550 --> 00:17:23,430
If you don't, I'll...

252
00:17:23,430 --> 00:17:24,390
Please, stop!

253
00:17:24,910 --> 00:17:28,620
There is no way that Gray-sama 
has betrayed Fairy Tail!

254
00:17:28,620 --> 00:17:30,500
Juvia believes in him!

255
00:17:30,500 --> 00:17:34,650
No matter what people say... Even if 
the whole world turned against him!

256
00:17:34,650 --> 00:17:36,070
Juvia...

257
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:39,380
Enough, Juvia.

258
00:17:39,940 --> 00:17:42,380
You're takin' me to Gramps, right?

259
00:17:42,380 --> 00:17:44,620
I don't think we have time to kill.

260
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:47,500
Follow me.

261
00:17:47,500 --> 00:17:50,580
We're making sure you 
don't try anything funny.

262
00:17:51,100 --> 00:17:52,230
Juvia...

263
00:17:53,280 --> 00:17:54,580
Gray-sama...

264
00:17:57,610 --> 00:17:58,750
Elfman!

265
00:17:58,750 --> 00:18:00,410
He should be fine now.

266
00:18:01,100 --> 00:18:02,360
Wendy!

267
00:18:02,360 --> 00:18:03,230
Wendy!

268
00:18:04,310 --> 00:18:08,990
I'm okay... I have to cure Wakaba-san 
and Macao-san soon, or...

269
00:18:08,990 --> 00:18:13,750
Stop it! If you use any more Sky 
Magic, your own life will be at risk!

270
00:18:14,500 --> 00:18:16,050
I don't care!

271
00:18:16,050 --> 00:18:17,470
Well, you should!

272
00:18:17,470 --> 00:18:19,430
I want to help everyone!

273
00:18:19,430 --> 00:18:22,950
Then I can really be a member of Fairy Tail!

274
00:18:25,580 --> 00:18:28,580
Sheesh, you're so stubborn...

275
00:18:32,820 --> 00:18:36,590
Everyone, please work 
together and save Natsu!

276
00:18:36,840 --> 00:18:40,900
Yeah. We all owe Natsu, big time.

277
00:18:40,900 --> 00:18:44,030
Yeah. When we were beat up by Phantom...

278
00:18:44,030 --> 00:18:48,020
Natsu fought for us back then.

279
00:18:48,020 --> 00:18:51,070
Natsu gave me courage!

280
00:18:51,070 --> 00:18:52,780
It's the same for everyone else, right?

281
00:18:52,780 --> 00:18:56,020
This time, we'll be the ones to save Natsu!

282
00:18:56,020 --> 00:19:00,030
All right! If we all work 
together, we can save Natsu!

283
00:19:00,030 --> 00:19:02,030
Aye, sir!

284
00:19:02,980 --> 00:19:04,060
Everyone...

285
00:19:05,190 --> 00:19:06,660
Wait!

286
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:09,460
Master!

287
00:19:09,970 --> 00:19:14,220
Fairy Tail is a guild that 
lives and dies with Magnolia.

288
00:19:14,650 --> 00:19:18,340
Our first priority is to protect 
the city from being destroyed!

289
00:19:19,010 --> 00:19:21,330
You want us to attack that thing?

290
00:19:21,330 --> 00:19:23,340
But Natsu is inside of it!

291
00:19:23,340 --> 00:19:27,140
As Master of Fairy Tail, I order you all:

292
00:19:27,380 --> 00:19:31,630
Use any means necessary 
to stop the Dragonoid!

293
00:19:31,920 --> 00:19:34,700
What? He'll be fine!

294
00:19:34,700 --> 00:19:37,020
His body's built nice and sturdy!

295
00:19:43,820 --> 00:19:44,530
Natsu!

296
00:19:46,900 --> 00:19:48,700
Can you hear me, Natsu?

297
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:52,340
You are not a wizard that would 
be done in by something like this!

298
00:19:53,830 --> 00:19:54,770
Erza...

299
00:19:56,350 --> 00:19:57,560
We...

300
00:19:59,380 --> 00:20:01,420
We are always like this.

301
00:20:01,950 --> 00:20:04,070
We communicated by fighting.

302
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:06,430
If you hadn't been there,

303
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:09,830
I would have already thrown away my life.

304
00:20:13,830 --> 00:20:16,140
I cannot lose you!

305
00:20:16,140 --> 00:20:17,460
No matter what!

306
00:20:17,460 --> 00:20:20,470
Natsu, I am going to bring you back with me!

307
00:20:41,890 --> 00:20:43,500
Daphne!

308
00:20:43,500 --> 00:20:45,180
Oh, too bad.

309
00:20:45,180 --> 00:20:46,680
Time's up.

310
00:21:04,460 --> 00:21:08,370
I'll stomp you flat, Erza Scarlet!

311
00:21:08,370 --> 00:21:09,620
Blast Bullet!

312
00:21:09,620 --> 00:21:11,520
Stinger Shoot!

313
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:14,950
Magic Card Explosion!

314
00:21:14,950 --> 00:21:16,210
Water Slicer!

315
00:21:16,210 --> 00:21:17,460
Sand Spear!

316
00:21:19,750 --> 00:21:22,110
Looks like it's started...

317
00:21:23,570 --> 00:21:25,970
Tell me why.

318
00:21:27,470 --> 00:21:30,810
I'll take full responsibility.

319
00:21:31,430 --> 00:21:33,580
I said, tell me why!

320
00:21:33,580 --> 00:21:34,610
Gray!

321
00:21:36,350 --> 00:21:42,220
Gramps... Only Natsu can 
defeat that Dragonoid!

322
00:21:43,440 --> 00:21:48,540
So the master decided that destroying 
the Dragonoid was the top priority?

323
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:50,140
What about Natsu?

324
00:21:50,140 --> 00:21:52,320
He said he was sturdily 
built, so he should be fine.

325
00:21:53,130 --> 00:21:54,040
Oh, I see.

326
00:21:54,700 --> 00:21:55,810
Natsu!

327
00:21:56,080 --> 00:22:00,450
On Master's orders, we will stop the 
Dragonoid with our full strength!

328
00:22:00,450 --> 00:22:03,530
Before we do that, I want to check with you!

329
00:22:04,310 --> 00:22:05,670
Let us hear you!

330
00:22:07,750 --> 00:22:10,510
Sure, I'll let you hear...

331
00:22:11,830 --> 00:22:12,890
Natsu...

332
00:22:12,890 --> 00:22:14,080
Ready?

333
00:22:14,080 --> 00:22:16,980
Cock an ear and listen up.

334
00:22:18,110 --> 00:22:22,000
Bust this thing up, and me along with it!

335
00:23:55,960 --> 00:24:00,980
No matter how far away, 
we'll come when you call!

336
00:24:00,980 --> 00:24:03,610
Whether it's searching for 
monsters or defeating monsters...

337
00:24:03,610 --> 00:24:06,500
Secret requests? Leave them to us!

338
00:24:06,500 --> 00:24:09,880
No matter what the problem, 
we'll solve it with one punch!

339
00:24:09,880 --> 00:24:11,100
What's that, you say?

340
00:24:11,100 --> 00:24:15,180
That's Fairy Tail in a nutshell!

341
00:24:15,180 --> 00:24:18,610
Next Time: Fairy Tail Wizards.

342
00:24:18,610 --> 00:24:19,720
Perfect!

343
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:23,020
Yeah, I think we should cut out your 
lines, Natsu. They get in the way.

344
00:24:23,020 --> 00:24:24,690
Huh? Did I say something wrong?

